[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/265] added some support for $nu
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/264] added 'to json'
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/262] added initial ctrl-c support
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/261] Made the history path more central
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/255] fixed par-each signature
, and improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/254] some iter perf improvements
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/253] fixed par-each example
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/252] added a simple parallel each
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/251] used different helper functions for split column
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/250] removed debug message
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/249] Pipeline data + capture
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/247] clippy fixes
