[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/260] added math avg
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/248] Engine q math(just one command)
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/259] worked on implementing the filters/last command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/246] cleaned up filesystem by moving get_interactive_confirmation into util.rs
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/245] updated readme with the issue 242 where people can sign up for commands to port
